💳 Credit Card Fraud Detector
A multilingual Streamlit app for credit card fraud detection with live currency conversion, flexible time units, and AI-powered risk analysis.

✨ Features
🌐 Supports English, Arabic (العربية), Spanish, French, Japanese

💱 Live currency conversion for USD, SAR, EUR, GBP, JPY (auto-updated)

⏱ Flexible time units: seconds, minutes, hours, days, weeks, months, years

🤖 Hybrid risk detection using model probability + rule-based checks

📊 Confidence score with risk levels: Low, Mid, High

🧾 Detailed transaction breakdown for audit purposes

📜 History table of checks (downloadable as CSV)

🇴 RTL layout support for Arabic

📄 Overview
This project uses a Logistic Regression model trained on credit-card transactions. Users enter an amount, pick a currency and time unit, and the app predicts whether the transaction is fraudulent, with confidence and risk level. It also keeps a downloadable audit history.

🧠 Machine Learning Details
Logistic Regression with class weighting for imbalance

StandardScaler for feature scaling

Percentile-based high-amount warning

Outputs a calibrated fraud probability

🛠 Tools and Technologies
Python, Streamlit

scikit-learn, pandas, numpy

matplotlib

Live FX via exchangerate.host

Custom i18n (EN/AR/ES/FR/JA)

