📥 Download Dataset & Model
These are not stored in the repo due to GitHub size limits. Download and place them as shown.

📄 Dataset: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1ZBFXuRGeV5NgqVMojrB66boYK5_u3enU?usp=sharing

🤖 Model & Pickle Files: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1MBObrwVyBV6vxMRxxLtyeUdpy0nB3NzZ?usp=sharing

Place them in:

project-root/
├─ data/
│  └─ creditcard.csv
└─ models/
   ├─ fraud_model.pkl
   ├─ fraud_scaler.pkl
   ├─ fraud_median_features.pkl
   └─ amount_99th_percentile.pkl

🚀 How to Run
pip install -r requirements.txt
python -m streamlit run app/app.py
